# Web portal only (not SSMP mobile)

This repo is the **public website mock-up**. Do **not** implement SSMP / mobile app features here.

## Build on the website

- UI/UX marketing pages, services, community content
- Mock **donation** flow (`/donate`) — FPX/DuitNow/card UI only
- Mock **course booking** (`/courses`)
- Mock **public event registration** (`/events`) — community-facing only
- Mock **volunteer interest** form (`/volunteer`)
- Emergency hotlines, contact, SEO metadata

## Do not build in this repo

- Member registration / activation
- Duty hour tracking, achievements, member dashboard
- SOS, admin/exco portals, approver workflows
- In-app event creation, push notifications, role-based member access
- Any “members portal” logged-in experience

The homepage may link to App Store / Google Play for **download only**. No mobile feature UI on the web.
